Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.76,0:01:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某一天  我突然受到召唤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.22,0:01:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就是个毫无特征的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.40,0:01:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像无色透明似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.11,0:01:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为透明  所以能被染成各种颜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.49,0:02:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我转移到许多人身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.49,0:02:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸收了他们的记忆与精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.17,0:02:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后  我成为了现在的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.96,0:02:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底  我就是人类的集合体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.05,0:02:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若这样的我是黑色的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.22,0:02:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这就是人类的本色了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.78,0:02:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就是安娜的生日了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.66,0:02:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.41,0:02:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂东
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.54,0:02:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个  明天别忘了带要送安娜的玫瑰花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.42,0:02:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.00,0:02:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了  回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.35,0:03:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天还真冷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.89,0:03:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完全进入冬天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.73,0:03:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬天可很忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.52,0:03:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等安娜的生日过完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.36,0:03:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有圣诞节跟新年派对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.53,0:03:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满满的派对可以玩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.24,0:03:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个派对控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.58,0:03:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天可别喝多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.54,0:03:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟安娜才是主角啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可得让安娜开心才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.17,0:03:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这次的惊喜派对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.96,0:03:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而害安娜替我们设想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.71,0:03:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做准备的这些天  安娜确实有故意躲着我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.35,0:03:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.10,0:03:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.93,0:03:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我加入吠舞罗前  过着狼狈不堪的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.31,0:04:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是对现在的幸福有点感慨罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.28,0:04:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛呀你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.20,0:04:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾利克你真是太可爱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.12,0:04:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦乖乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.54,0:04:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里你不介意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这里也可以吧  - 别再闹我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.71,0:04:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待明天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.13,0:04:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.15,0:04:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  心情这么好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.15,0:04:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.99,0:04:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想明天应该能久违地和大家在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.80,0:05:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尊  安娜睡了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.72,0:05:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.22,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么王  这给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天把这个送给她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝她生日快乐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.82,0:05:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然这么听话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天中午以前  你要负责拖住安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.49,0:05:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们则趁这段期间准备派对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.16,0:05:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草薙哥  有什么需要帮忙的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.75,0:05:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有需要帮忙的话也算我一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.50,0:05:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.50,0:05:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你帮忙收一下那边的盘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.38,0:05:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.55,0:05:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镰本  那边的你负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.84,0:05:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.22,0:05:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么等我忙完了就回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.10,0:05:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忙完？你有什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.77,0:06:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我准备了一个特大蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.82,0:06:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是做不出来的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.65,0:06:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.78,0:06:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得之前看到的“蜡烛”光芒吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.62,0:06:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得那些蜡烛就像是插在城市这个巨大蛋糕上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.75,0:06:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这虽然不是什么像样的生日礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.84,0:06:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但明天我想让安娜看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.59,0:06:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天可别睡过头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.79,0:07:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明厌上午我会去拿预订的生日蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.21,0:07:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家路上小心点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.31,0:07:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.90,0:07:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜色真美不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了拍夜景而来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.74,0:07:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问你是来做什么的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.16,0:07:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫十束多多良  你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.93,0:07:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我乃第七王权者  无色之王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里等人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.27,0:08:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说这里夜色很美？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.98,0:08:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  确实挺美的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.96,0:08:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.54,0:08:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你无怨无仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.59,0:08:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  其实我跟谁都无怨无仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.39,0:08:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你还是得死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.01,0:08:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我才能成为“唯一”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.53,0:08:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七个王的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.82,0:08:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七条道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.99,0:09:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七个故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.58,0:09:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些东西  就全都由我吞噬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.73,0:09:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶紧回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.77,0:09:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回大家那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.30,0:09:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我还是得死吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.85,0:10:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.44,0:10:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然对方是无色之王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.11,0:10:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许还会对其他同伴出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.49,0:10:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.45,0:10:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下要给大家添麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.11,0:11:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.54,0:11:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草薙哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.75,0:11:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  十束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.75,0:11:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.75,0:11:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草薙哥  怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.38,0:11:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八田你也一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.09,0:11:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十束出事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.77,0:11:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这种时候了  还想着这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.94,0:11:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样算不算薄情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.90,0:11:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十束  你不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.29,0:11:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草薙哥  你听得见吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.79,0:11:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到居然喷得这么夸张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.80,0:12:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你怎么这么爱乱来  - 很痛的啊  草薙哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.06,0:12:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬吠舞罗酒吧重新开张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.27,0:12:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.83,0:12:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.79,0:12:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要坐云霄飞车趁现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.99,0:12:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我看是八田自己想坐吧  - 我看还是不要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.25,0:12:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这蝴蝶一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.34,0:12:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我过得很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.26,0:12:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.94,0:12:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使现在也这么认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.36,0:12:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个蠢蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.28,0:13:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.74,0:13:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我没机会对安娜说生日快乐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.13,0:13:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会生我的气呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.05,0:13:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.32,0:13:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等著  我们马上就到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.37,0:13:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.21,0:13:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是这样的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.71,0:14:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空还是这么美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.45,0:14:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多多良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.21,0:14:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  尊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.96,0:14:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个坏消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.96,0:14:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十束哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.94,0:15:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在人在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.61,0:15:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你待着别动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.98,0:15:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万别离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.07,0:15:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会带十束来找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.87,0:15:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十束他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.51,0:15:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.59,0:16:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.73,0:16:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八田…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.13,0:16:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说有吠舞罗的干部遇害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.01,0:16:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.34,0:16:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有民众听到枪声报警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.55,0:17:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有人目击到两名男子疑似在搬运遗体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.39,0:17:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察已经展开调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.10,0:17:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但吠舞罗的草薙先生向淡岛汇报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.48,0:17:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.36,0:17:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死者是十束多多良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.86,0:17:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶手自称无色之王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.16,0:17:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是氏族之间的纠纷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.96,0:17:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤之氏族会自行了断  不容外人插手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.71,0:17:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…他是这么说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.00,0:17:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是劝不动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.67,0:17:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之  这不是警察能处理的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.35,0:17:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经请他们收手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我们接手侦办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.02,0:17:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这案子非常严重吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.61,0:17:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有什么差错…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.28,0:17:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  所以绝不能出差错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.82,0:18:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会逮捕凶手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.25,0:18:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟不能让扰乱秩序的人逍遥法外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.09,0:18:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更不能坐视他们动用极有可能危及数十万生命的私刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.76,0:18:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找出凶手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.85,0:18:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾等大义  毫无阴霾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.40,0:18:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.99,0:18:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.49,0:18:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无色之王的天下吞拼游戏开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.20,0:18:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你接下来还会继续介入吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.71,0:18:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这次我只负责支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.29,0:18:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是属于新任无色之王的游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.01,0:19:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是正好能为接下来的游戏怖局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.31,0:19:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以给了点协助和建议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.48,0:19:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我并不打算打扰他玩游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.61,0:19:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道接下来会如何发展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.15,0:19:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是那位赤王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.75,0:19:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磐叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.71,0:19:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是觉得不忍心  你可以不必观战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.59,0:19:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还能做的  也就只剩观战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.47,0:19:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤王应该会选择自己的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.90,0:19:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不只赤王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.19,0:19:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有拥有力量的人  都该凭自己的力量选择出路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.53,0:20:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是这世界应有的姿态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.16,0:20:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拭目以待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.37,0:20:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.92,0:20:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葬礼怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.05,0:21:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没有其他亲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.01,0:21:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要下葬的话只能靠我们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.01,0:21:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.35,0:21:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来火葬他吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.60,0:21:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.15,0:21:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是十束的耳环吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.86,0:21:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它本来就有那红光的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.82,0:21:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里头是空的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.41,0:21:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你装了什么进去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.00,0:21:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那红色该不会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.92,0:21:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是烧到血、骨、灰都不剩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.55,0:21:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连个墓都造不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.68,0:21:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才用那代替墓碑吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.98,0:21:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草薙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.11,0:21:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.82,0:22:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该结清这笔账了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.49,0:22:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会说让你看开点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.24,0:22:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者顺其自然之类的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.20,0:22:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以什么都不说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.92,0:22:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我喜欢这样的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.33,0:22:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你  十束还有吠舞罗的成员一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.96,0:22:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家设法共度难关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.71,0:22:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年少轻狂地待在一起胡闹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.64,0:22:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切的一切  都还挺不赖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.56,0:22:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是该了断这一切了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.36,0:23:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No BIood
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.37,0:23:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No Bone
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.54,0:23:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No Ash
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.95,0:24:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.08,0:25:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管谁是死是生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.25,0:25:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海总是如此超然  美得让人火大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.18,0:25:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我过得很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.22,0:25:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…这是那小子的遗言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.85,0:25:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这样危险的王是需要一个容身之地的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:31.69,0:25:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个让你睡睡午觉吃个饭  有时还能找个乐子的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.66,0:25:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是为了你  而是为了世人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.41,0:25:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世人关我什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:45.71,0:25:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就当是为了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.97,0:25:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…那些就到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:57.35,0:25:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.77,0:26:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十束他选择了属于自己的无悔一生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:10.65,0:26:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要那么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:18.95,0:26:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:07.75,0:27:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.71,0:27:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去报仇吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:19.93,0:27:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没那么冠冕堂皇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:23.93,0:27:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是做我想做的事
